high_descs: Turn around, walk to the sink, turn left to the counter by the stove
Grab the egg in front of the toaster
Turn around, walk to the microwave
Open the microwave, put the egg in it, close the microwave, turn it on, open the microwave, take the egg out, close the microwave
Turn around, walk to the sink
Put the egg in the sink on the left
anns.task_desc: Heat the egg with microwave, put the egg in the sink

high_descs: Turn around, go toward the sink, and then turn left at the counter to the right of the stove.
Pick up the egg from in front of the toaster.
Turn around and go to the microwave in front of you.
Heat the egg in the microwave.
Turn around, then go right to reach the sink.
Place the egg in the left sink basin.
anns.task_desc: Put a cooked egg in the sink.

high_descs: Turn around and make your way over to the spot on the counter directly to the right of the stove between the stove and the toaster.
Pick up the egg that's near the toaster.
Turn around and walk to the microwave.
Cook the egg in the microwave and then take it back out and close the door to the microwave.
Walk over to the left sink.
Put the egg into the left sink.
anns.task_desc: Put a microwaved egg in the sink.
